    "content": "<div class=\"about-page-wrapper\">\n\n    <!-- Mission Statement -->\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 60px; text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">We're building the operating system for the future.</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.25rem; color: #a1a1aa; line-height: 1.6;\">Gaia Alpha was born from a simple idea: Enterprise software doesn't have to be complicated. We believe in the power of simplicity, the speed of vanilla code, and the freedom of open source.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <hr style=\"border: 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin: 60px 0;\" />\n\n    <!-- Our Story & Vision Grid -->\n    <section style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 80px;\">\n        <div>\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #fff;\">Our Story</h3>\n            <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Founded in 2024, Gaia Alpha started as an experiment to see if we could build a full-stack framework without the bloat of modern toolchains. What began as a lightweight prototype quickly evolved into a robust ecosystem used by forward-thinking teams to deploy applications in record time.</p>\n            <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa; line-height: 1.7;\">Today, we are a global community of developers, designers, and dreamers working together to redefine what's possible on the web.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"Team working together\" style=\"width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Values -->\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 80px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 50px; color: #fff;\">Our Core Values</h3>\n        <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;\">\n            <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 15px;\">‚ö°</div>\n                <h4 style=\"font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #fff;\">Radical Simplicity</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa;\">We ruthlessly eliminate complexity. If it doesn't add value, it doesn't belong in the codebase.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 15px;\">üîì</div>\n                <h4 style=\"font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #fff;\">Open by Default</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa;\">Transparancy builds trust. We build in public and empower our community to contribute.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 15px;\">ü§ù</div>\n                <h4 style=\"font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #fff;\">Users First</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa;\">Technology serves people, not the other way around. Every decision starts with the user experience.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Team -->\n    <section>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 50px; color: #fff;\">Meet the Team</h3>\n        <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; text-align: center;\">\n            <div>\n                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/300?u=a042581f4e29026024d\" alt=\"CEO\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 2px solid #6366f1;\">\n                <h4 style=\"color: #fff; margin-bottom: 5px;\">Alex Rivera</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem;\">Founder & CEO</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/300?u=a042581f4e29026704d\" alt=\"CTO\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 2px solid #10b981;\">\n                <h4 style=\"color: #fff; margin-bottom: 5px;\">Sarah Chen</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem;\">CTO</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/300?u=a04258114e29026302d\" alt=\"Designer\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 2px solid #f59e0b;\">\n                <h4 style=\"color: #fff; margin-bottom: 5px;\">Marcus Johnson</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem;\">Lead Designer</p>\n            </div>\n             <div>\n                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/300?u=a042581f4e29026024a\" alt=\"Developer\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 2px solid #ec4899;\">\n                <h4 style=\"color: #fff; margin-bottom: 5px;\">Elena Rodriguez</h4>\n                <p style=\"color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem;\">Senior Eng.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n</div>",
